Package functional.genericKeywords

Interface GenericKeywordsInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
FileUtilities, GenericKeywords, TestExecutionEngine
public interface GenericKeywordsInterface
Interface defining generic web automation keywords. This interface provides methods for various web automation tasks such as clicking elements, inputting text, navigating, and verifying conditions.
